content: Pennsylvania is my closest swing state.  How do I find out what is needed on the ground?  I prefer not to make calls this time  around.

Hi <@1277630108127199437> I encourage you to get the PA role, then you can ask the folks in that channel. You can get your new fole by going to Channels & Roles near the top of your left menu. Also you can search on https://events.democrats.org, put the city, zip or state in the location to see events close by.
Here's a link to our PA Victory site on Mobilize. https://www.mobilize.us/2024pavictory/?tag_ids=3274
